      <title>Focus Financial Partners 推迟 36.5 亿美元定期贷款交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/focus-financial-partners-postpones-3-65-billion-term-loan-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于最近几天全球市场的动荡抑制了债务市场的发行，Focus Financial Partners 的 36.5 亿美元定期贷款计划已被推迟，这是本周美国杠杆贷款交易遭遇的第三次推迟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/focus-financial-partners-postpones-3-65-billion-term-loan-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 14:34:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
